<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TileMap Editor - Tutorial</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main">
        <div class="main__article">
            <h1 class="main__article_title">How to:</h1>
            <ul class="main__list">
                <li>
                    <a href="#1" class="main__list_item_link">
                        change tile
                    </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="#2" class="main__list_item_link">
                        set location name
                    </a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <hr class="main__line" />

        <div class="main__article" id="1">
            <h3 class="main__article_title">
                How to change the tile
            </h3>
            <p>
                First, select the image from "Select Tile" menu on the
                left side of the screen
            </p>
            <img
                src="/img/select-tile.png"
                alt="Tile selection menu"
                class="main__article_image"
            />
            <p>
                In the next step, left click on the tile you want to
                change.
            </p>
            <img
                src="/img/change-tile.png"
                alt="Editor fragment"
                class="main__article_image"
            />
        </div>

        <hr class="main__line" />

        <div class="main__article" id="2">
            <h3 class="main__article_title">
                Set location name
            </h3>
            <p>
                Switch to the overlay layer and right click on the tile
                in the place you want to matk on the map.
            </p>
            <img
                src="/img/select-layer.png"
                alt="Layer selection menu"
                class="main__article_image"
            />
            <p>
                In the next step, left click on the tile you want to
                change.
            </p>
            <img
                src="/img/set-location.png"
                alt="Location name input"
                class="main__article_image"
            />
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>